
The purpose of the project is to provide a way to manage large scale environments within an cloud/virtualized infrastructure. The target platform will be the following:

* Redhat
* Fedora
* Centos

Some projects is may rely on are:

* Cobbler
* Facter

The main features will be:

* Configuration management for applications
* Allowing a machine to get an inventory list of what should be installed
* Application vs Master keys for authentication
* Event based configuration updates
* Stereotyping for a large environment
* Infrastructure definition and management


The main language will be python
